title: Shares of the iPhone maker soar amid the AI frenzy, setting a record high.
description: Amid an intense AI frenzy, shares of Hon Hai Precision Industry Co.—also referred to as the iPhone Maker because of its affiliation with Apple Inc.—have reached previously unheard-of heights.
